OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780603551
OL,3,CGang convicted of smuggling migrants
OL,4,Cthrough Channel Tunnel
OL,6,FAn organised crime gang, fronted by
OL,7,FKent-based career criminal Freddy
OL,8,FLawrence, has been convicted of
OL,9,Fsmuggling Afghan migrants into the UK
OL,10,Finside a specially adapted truck.
OL,12,FFollowing a trial at the Old Bailey on
OL,13,FWednesday 3rd June, the jury found
OL,14,FRohit Chawla and Terry Brewer guilty
OL,15,Fof conspiring to facilitate illegal
OL,16,Fimmigration.
OL,18,FGroup ringleader Mark Youell was found
OL,19,Fguilty of the same charge, alongside
OL,20,Fmoney laundering, on the 27th May.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
