OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780603551
OL,3,CGang convicted of smuggling migrants
OL,4,Cthrough Channel Tunnel
OL,6,FA fourth member, Carl Bailey, had
OL,7,Falready pleaded guilty to his
OL,8,Finvolvement, while a fifth defendant
OL,9,Fsaw the jury fail to reach a verdict.
OL,11,FWATCH: Moment police discover 12
OL,12,Fmigrants, including a child, hidden
OL,13,Fbehind a false bulkhead in the back of
OL,14,Fthe lorry.
OL,16,FThe National Crime Agency (NCA) first
OL,17,Fspotted Youell, 69, and Bailey, 52,
OL,18,Fwhen they met with Freddy Lawrence in
OL,19,FJuly 2019.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780603551
OL,3,CGang convicted of smuggling migrants
OL,4,Cthrough Channel Tunnel
OL,6,FLawrence was later jailed for seven-
OL,7,Fand-a-half years for a separate people-
OL,8,Fsmuggling offence in January 2025.
OL,10,FSurveillance officers tracked the gang
OL,11,Fas they coordinated with father-and-
OL,12,Fson Rohit and Surjeet Chawla, who both
OL,13,Fhad prior convictions for people
OL,14,Fsmuggling.
OL,16,FIn September 2019, officers moved in
OL,17,Fon the gang's lorry at Osterley
OL,18,FCricket Club in west London.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780603551
OL,3,CGang convicted of smuggling migrants
OL,4,Cthrough Channel Tunnel
OL,6,FHidden behind a false bulkhead in a
OL,7,Fspecially constructed concealment,
OL,8,Fauthorities discovered 12 Afghan Sikh
OL,9,Fmigrants, including one child.
OL,11,FPhone records revealed the truck had
OL,12,Ftraveled from Purfleet to France the
OL,13,Fprevious day, returning to Folkestone
OL,14,Fvia the Channel Tunnel.
OL,16,FGang member Terry Brewer, 51, acted as
OL,17,Fthe link between Bailey and the
OL,18,Fdrivers. Days after the truck was
OL,19,Fintercepted, Bailey and Youell met up
OL,20,Fwith the Chawlas.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780603551
OL,3,CGang convicted of smuggling migrants
OL,4,Cthrough Channel Tunnel
OL,6,FShortly after the meeting, officers
OL,7,Farrested Bailey and Youell just after
OL,8,Fthey had received a carrier bag
OL,9,Fcontaining #65,000 in cash - their
OL,10,Fpayment for organising the trip.
OL,12,FThe Chawlas were arrested in mid-to-
OL,13,Flate 2020. Surjeet Chawla died in
OL,14,FDecember 2022 before he could stand
OL,15,Ftrial.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780603551
OL,3,CGang convicted of smuggling migrants
OL,4,Cthrough Channel Tunnel
OL,6,FJacque Beer, NCA Regional Head of
OL,7,FInvestigations, said the gang saw an
OL,8,Fopportunity to make money out of the
OL,9,Fdesperation of others: "They clearly
OL,10,Fdid not care about the safety or
OL,11,Fsecurity of the men, women and
OL,12,Fchildren they were transporting, just
OL,13,Fseeing them as an extra way to make
OL,14,Fmore money."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780603551
OL,3,CGang convicted of smuggling migrants
OL,4,Cthrough Channel Tunnel
OL,6,FGiorgina Venturella from the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service (CPS) added that
OL,8,Fphone records were vital in tracking
OL,9,Fthe gang's journeys and proving how
OL,10,Fthey worked together: "Those involved
OL,11,Fin organised immigration crime cannot
OL,12,Fevade detection by using burner phones
OL,13,For changing numbers. The evidence in
OL,14,Fthis case shows how law enforcement
OL,15,Fcan piece together their activities."
OL,17,FMark Youell, who was separately
OL,18,Fconvicted in 2021 for importing Class
OL,19,FA drugs, will be sentenced alongside
OL,20,FChawla and Brewer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
