OL,3,CGang convicted of smuggling migrants
OL,4,Cthrough Channel Tunnel
OL,6,FA sentencing date is expected to be
OL,7,Fset at a hearing on June 10.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
